+	 *
+	 * <p>Upon return:
+	 * <ul><li>SUCCESS/PASS passes on the callback to the next listener
+	 * <li>CONSUME continues the default code for breaking the block and ignores all other listeners
+	 * <li>FAIL cancels the block breaking action</ul>
